{"tid":2323805,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本第一牛郎驚見「高中時最害怕的人」羅蘭直呼：好可怕！","createTime":"2020-12-13T12:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T13:08:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c34e4b9f4ad2f1cdc97e377ee6a8ebd5250377","tid":2323805,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"「日本第一牛郎」封號的羅蘭（Roland），原名松尾風雅的他充滿超高自信風格引起正、反兩極的評價，他曾在武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）前期來台，到夜市時沒戴口罩，還直說：「新冠狀肺炎應該要怕我才對」如此狂妄言論引發一陣譁然，然而他所開的牛郎店卻不敵疫情沒生意而關閉，不過他仍有許多投資項目，近日他YouTube竟上傳了一位他高中時「最害怕的人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/13/2933221-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2F2933221-PH.jpg&h=7b9a1853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「日本第一牛郎」羅蘭人氣相當高。（圖／翻攝自羅蘭IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/13/2933223-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2F2933223-PH.jpg&h=23f6a192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲羅蘭在影片表示高中時期開始踢足球。（圖／翻攝自羅蘭YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/13/2933234-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2F2933234-PH.jpg&h=9168f87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲羅蘭所拍攝的高中足球雜誌封面非常具代表性。（圖／翻攝自羅蘭IG）<br />\n<br />\n先前他為一本雜誌拍足球封面，擁有182公分高挺的身高的他，曾在小學生演講引起一陣旋風，這次親自開車回到自己的母校帝京高中，他表示自己當時很喜歡踢足球，甚至期待靠足球得到女生關注，不過後來因為技術不過關的關係，沒有成為正式隊員，現在陰錯陽差反而成為人氣男公關，至今仍舊非常愛踢足球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/13/2933260-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2F2933260-PH.jpg&h=b912fcec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲羅蘭高中時期「最害怕的人」突登場。（圖／翻攝自羅蘭YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n沒想到在影片中途，他高中時期「最害怕的人」突然出場，原來是羅蘭的高中足球教練「廣瀨教練」驚喜現身，雖然羅蘭現在氣場相當強大，然而他見到教練時，整個人也突然龜縮「乖」了起來，對方還想揍羅蘭，讓他大呼好可怕：「請您不要這樣」和以往的風格大相逕庭，笑歪了網友與粉絲們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/13/2933237-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F13%2F2933237-PH.jpg&h=088a9e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲原來是羅蘭高中時期的足球教練。（圖／翻攝自羅蘭YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n▼【羅蘭頻道】（影片來自YouTube，若遭移除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tIyBhgaL93I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtIyBhgaL93I&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mb6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=a4eacf46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tIyBhgaL93I</a>"},{"pid":"5ead4985db1077fb192d862b4360cd1f487802ae","tid":2323805,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"羅蘭7.7"},{"pid":"bd4d20af36616a5963ecc0de0e62da6b0857255a","tid":2323805,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ead4985db1077fb192d862b4360cd1f487802ae","tid":2323805,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"羅蘭7.7"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"亂up 24<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25207fd86f2167930fed68bae4bdbb2f67ed069","tid":2323805,"uid":89608,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"日本文化真係幾得意,<br />\n咁都可以變到出位到去學校演講, <br />\n即係鼓勵小朋友去做,<br />\n可能問題又真係唔係咁大既, 搵到錢就得啦"},{"pid":"b3f8beeda0a5386ed839ee69c8c8b901c9f96fee","tid":2323805,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"戴超真係好重要"},{"pid":"fdcc55e2bc29ae419f5692dab9dbbaac131a1158","tid":2323805,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"食波餅咪死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62527450903766d08a8ed8e02e337d82a4b88be","tid":2323805,"uid":4917,"like":